snippet.title: FLORENCE | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on the App Store: http://florencegame.com and Google Play Store: http://bit.ly/Florence_Android

Florence is an interactive storybook from the award-winning lead designer of Monument Valley about the heart-racing highs and heartbreaking lows of a young woman's very first love.

Developed by MOUNTAINS. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2018
